reviewText: I started watching this DVD and before the first 5 minutes was done, I had to turn it off.  It is a documentary and was not at all what I expected.

This promised lots, the official blurb offered a tantalising insight into a world of sex and the anonymous men who often fill that world, but what you get, in my opinion, is a poorly edited mish mash of faceless male genitalia with porn type over dubbing and in some cases subtitles to cover the poor recording. A complete waste of money.
Why disguise the voices if the faces aren't shown?!?! It was eye-opening, disgusting and kinky all at the same time. Sound effects were less than desirable. A for effort!
